name: CNContainerType
desc: The container may be local on the device or associated with a server account that has contacts.

items.name: case local
items.desc: A container for contacts only stored locally on the device. There is only one local container for a device.

items.name: case exchange
items.desc: A container for contacts stored in an Exchange folder from an Exchange server.

items.name: case cardDAV
items.desc: A container for contacts stored in an CardDAV server, such as iCloud.
